HOUSE BILL 1226 11
1 PHYSICALLY LOCATED IN THE STATE SUBMITS TO THE JURISDICTION OF THE STATE
2 COURTS FOR ENFORCEMENT UNDER THIS SUBTITLE.
3 (D) THE CHAIR OF THE COMMISSION MAY CONSULT WITH THE ATTORNEY
