1 FINE OF $50,000 FOR A FIRST VIOLATION AND $100,000 FOR EACH SUBSEQUENT
2 VIOLATION.
3 (II) EACH ILLEGAL ONLINE GAMBLING TRANSACTION THAT IS
4 PROCESSED AND EACH ACT OF SUPPORT OF ILLEGAL ONLINE GAMBLING
